release_note: Hi guys! Thank you all for downloading and using COMO Bujo . This time we have updated the following features: Custom support for setting check in flags Added 4 small sized habit widgets 2 medium sized habit widgets and 3 large sized habit widgets Add blessing emoticons and stickers Fix known bugs If you have any questions or suggestions please leave a comment in the store or email us at panxingxing07 163.com! We will continue to add new features in subsequent versions so stay tuned! Development is not easy. If you think our application is great please don t forget to give us a five star rating!
